<p><strong><span>国庆中秋</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>“超长黄金周”</span></strong><strong><span>假期已过半程，</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>有没有算算假期这几天</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>你花了多钱？</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201006/aa81b26e95a3419fbc166f10bd3fecde.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>来自陕西省商务厅的监测的最新数据，</span></strong></p>
<p><span><strong><span>今年国庆前五天，</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><span>陕西商品销售实现292.8亿元，</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><span>同比增长8%以上，</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><span>其中商品零售255.8亿元，</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><span>餐饮收入37亿元！</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201006/8138bcb966de4e678c0a885f5fd6df95.gif" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
